📘 FLAG IDENTIFIER AI
=========================

A deep learning–based web app that predicts the country name of a flag using a trained CNN model and a dataset of 224 countries.

────────────────────────────────────────────
📁 PROJECT STRUCTURE
────────────────────────────────────────────
| File / Folder                         | Description                                 |
|--------------------------------------|---------------------------------------------|
| app.py                               | Main Flask backend application               |
| templates/index.html                 | HTML frontend interface                      |
| static/                              | Folder to store uploaded images              |
| flag_model.h5                        | Trained CNN model file                       |
| country-flags-in-the-wild/train/     | Flag images organized by 224 country folders |
| README.txt / README.md               | Project documentation                        |

────────────────────────────────────────────
🛠️ TECHNOLOGIES USED
────────────────────────────────────────────
| Component     | Technology             |
|---------------|------------------------|
| Language      | Python 3.9+            |
| Framework     | Flask                  |
| ML Library    | TensorFlow, Keras      |
| Image Utils   | Pillow                 |
| Others        | NumPy, HTML/CSS        |

